GLUTEN FREE PARADISE!
This place doesn't have just small a gluten free menu...it literally can substitute almost anything on the menu into G-Free.
From what I could tell the ravioli and lasagna were the only two things I couldn't accommodate.
Nice ambiance, the food was pretty good, and it was clean, which is an important factor for me.
The food came out very quickly as well, however it was lunch time and not very busy.
I will definitely be back...if not for anything then the fact that for a change I can look at an entire menu!

